---
title: Striploin Steak au Poivre with Bacon Caesar Salad and Fries
description: On the menu tonight is a premium steakhouse classic that is sure to warm the soul. Juicy striploin steak is adorned with an umami-filled pepper sauce and paired with a creamy Caesar salad and oven fries. It's a delicious meal you won't soon forget.

